OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780323077
OL,3,CBadenoch criticises British Museum for
OL,4,Cdelaying Jewish event over protest
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,FKemi Badenoch has criticised the
OL,8,FBritish Museum for postponing a talk
OL,9,Fon Jewish culture because of potential
OL,10,Fprotests.
OL,12,FThe museum said it had postponed the
OL,13,Fevent after being told a "significant
OL,14,Fproportion" of attendees were planning
OL,15,Fto disrupt it.
OL,17,FThe lecture on ancient Israel and
OL,18,FJudah was due to take place on
OL,19,FThursday afternoon as part of Jewish
OL,20,FCulture Month.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@KO]
