FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780323077
OL,3,CBadenoch criticises British Museum for
OL,4,Cdelaying Jewish event over protest
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,FThe British Museum said in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "In recent days, we were
OL,9,Finformed that a significant proportion
OL,10,Fof registered attendees were
OL,11,Findividuals intending to deliberately
OL,12,Fdisrupt the event, preventing others
OL,13,Ffrom participating in good faith and
OL,14,Fundermining the purpose of the
OL,15,Fprogramme.
OL,17,F"The British Museum fully recognises
OL,18,Fthe importance of lawful protest and
OL,19,Ffreedom of expression in a democratic
OL,20,Fsociety.
OL,26,@pD@LOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780323077
OL,3,CBadenoch criticises British Museum for
OL,4,Cdelaying Jewish event over protest
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,F"Equally, we have a responsibility to
OL,8,Fensure that events hosted within the
OL,9,Fmuseum can proceed safely, securely
OL,10,Fand without intimidation for speakers,
OL,11,Fstaff and visitors alike.
OL,13,F"Following discussions with organisers
OL,14,Fand security partners, a joint
OL,15,Fdecision was taken to postpone the
OL,16,Fevent to a later date when it can take
OL,17,Fplace in an environment that properly
OL,18,Fsafeguards both the audience
OL,19,Fexperience and the integrity of the
OL,20,Fprogramme itself."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
