FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780323077
OL,3,CBadenoch criticises British Museum for
OL,4,Cdelaying Jewish event over protest
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,FThe decision was taken "to protect the
OL,8,Fevent ` not to diminish it", the
OL,9,Fmuseum added.
OL,11,FConservative Party leader Mrs Badenoch
OL,12,Furged Sir Keir Starmer's Government to
OL,13,Fintervene and tell the museum to "do
OL,14,Fwhat's necessary" for the event to go
OL,15,Fahead.
OL,17,FShe said: "Jewish Culture Month is
OL,18,Fmeant to promote awareness of and
OL,19,Fcelebrate Jewish culture in the UK.
OL,20,FThis decision achieves precisely the
OL,21,Fopposite.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@[O]uD@bOUvD@QO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
