PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780323077
OL,3,CBadenoch criticises British Museum for
OL,4,Cdelaying Jewish event over protest
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,F"Jewish acts and actors are now being
OL,8,Froutinely cancelled from events across
OL,9,Fthe UK. As with the marches and
OL,10,Fprotests going past synagogues and
OL,11,Fknocking on doors intimidating Jews,
OL,12,Fthe end result is an erasure of Jews
OL,13,Fand Jewish culture from Britain's
OL,14,Fpublic space.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
