PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780323077
OL,3,CBadenoch criticises British Museum for
OL,4,Cdelaying Jewish event over protest
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,F"The Government says it wants to
OL,8,Fcombat antisemitism, it needs to tell
OL,9,Fpublicly funded institutions like the
OL,10,FBritish Museum to do what's necessary
OL,11,Fto put this event on. The
OL,12,FConservatives will always make sure
OL,13,Fthat Britain feels a safe place for
OL,14,FJews."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
